name: Eligible applicants for funds
text: [Section effective July 1, 2006.  For section effective until June 30, 2006, see above.]  Eligible applicants for funds shall include nonprofit and for-profit corporations, limited liability companies, partnerships, and government agencies, who are qualified in accordance with rules adopted by the administration pursuant to chapter 91. [L 1997, c 350, pt of §2; am L 2005, c 196, §§6, 26(a)]
